Google Dorking, also known as Google Hacking, is a technique that utilizes advanced search operators to uncover information on the internet that may not be readily available through standard search queries.
Name published in Google Hacking Database(GHDB) for Files Containing Juicy Info .  ( https://www.exploit-db.com/google-hacking-database?author=12083 )

Acknowledge by NCIIPC for reporting sites that are vulnerable to email spoofing. Common attack used for phising.  

